[section#expr.or
    [:en] Bitwise inclusive OR operator
    [:zh_CN] 按位或运算符

[:en]
[%expression[!bitwise inclusive OR]]
[%operator[!bitwise inclusive OR]]
[%[`|][%operator[!bitwise inclusive OR]]]
[:zh_CN]
[%表达式[!按位或～]]
[%运算符[!按位或～]]
[%[`|][%运算符[!按位或～]]]
]

[syntax]
[rule inclusive-or-expression [:zh_CN] 或表达式 ]
    [| exclusive-or-expression ]
    [| inclusive-or-expression [`|] exclusive-or-expression ]
[rule:end]
[syntax:end]

[para]
[:en]
The usual arithmetic conversions ([#expr.arith.conv]) are performed; the result
is the bitwise inclusive [$:sc OR] function of its operands.
[:zh_CN]
实施一般算术转换（[#expr.arith.conv]）；其结果为操作数的按位或函数。

[:en]
The operator applies only to integral or unscoped enumeration operands.
[:zh_CN]
该运算符仅适用于整型或无作用域枚举操作数。
